sections.content: The property covered under Gift Settlement Deed No. 731 of 2026 dated 29/Jan/2026, executed by Nakka Rambabu in favour of his Elder Son, Nakka Praveen Kumar, towards the property admeasuring an extent of 122.77 Sq. Yds, bearing house number 2-81, comprised in survey number 129-4, situated in Tandavapalle Village and Grama Panchayat, Amalapuram Mandal, within the District of Konaseema registered at sub-registrar office Amalapuram(414) is bounded as follows: North by: Road South by: Site of Pithani Satyanarayana East by: Donnor site West by: Site and RCC slab House of Nakka Syamalarao Note:: Schedule property is part of Gramakantam as per deed.
It is noted from the given documents and EC that the schedule property is not part of any active Mortgage or Lease Deed.

Note:: It is to be noted that the online EC has been verified using the key parameters, namely the Document Number, Survey Number/House Number, and Split Survey/House Number of the concerned SRO, as per the Deed. However, cross-verification across multiple SROs has not been carried out due to the AP portal’s requirement of separate passwords for each search parameter, and the OTP-based authentication mechanism makes searches across multiple SROs operationally infeasible.
